      "content": "woah ok that sounds pretty intense. i'm just really hesitant because the clinic is so expensive and i really don't want to deal with all that if it's just a sprain. are you sure i can't just take some extra ibuprofen and keep it elevated for like a week before deciding? i've seen people do that and be totally fine.",
